ServerName: ProjectMoney ServerBase: Devolution V7 Progress: 5-10% Hello I am here to inform you on my progress of our new server ProjectMoney. Mrmoney and I (Rubiks Cube) and have started a server/client.
[size=12pt][u][i][b]Features:[/b][/i][/u][/size]
-Full Team PK Area -Full Edge Pking! -All four Godswords! -Specs on all weapons as in normal RuneScape -Full ele' and all new items fully working! -Dark bow, etc. give range exp unlike in HiyaScape V2 -2-3 MiniGames -New Stating Area! -New Training Area! -New Fishing Area! -New Shopping Area -All SkillCapes! -Over 30 Shops All Over -Very Own Client [color=green]-Sweet "explosion -Cool Fire"[/color] -Being coded well, not a cheap 1 hour code.
[size=11pt][b]PLEASE POST IF YOU HAVE ANY IDEAS OR REQUEST![/b][/size]
